</head><body><table border=0 align=center width=80%><tr><td class=textbody><center><h1>Pillar of Frost</h1><br>by Gemdiver of Fennin Ro</center><br><div align="center">
  <center>
  <table border=0 width=640 style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td>
    This is a quick and easy way to get the spell Pillar of Frost, a spell 
    crucial to quadding in the Plane of Fire and other high level zones.<br>
&nbsp;<hr>
    <p>Go into Toxxulia Forest and search for a Kobold Caster. It's a rare spawn 
    and only appears on the far side of the bridge from Erudin. He will drop 
    half of a scroll. </p>
    <p>Take the scroll to Josper Kenshed who you can find inside of Erudin and 
    give it to him. He will give you the
    <a href="http://www.graffe.com/spells.php?name=pillar+of+frost">Pillar of 
    Frost spell</a>.</p>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>&nbsp;</td></tr></table></center>
